         <div type="translation">
            <ab>... thirty-six drachmas of silver, total 36 dr. silver, and four quarter of gold, total 4 qrs. gold, on condition that she (?) annuls with me our contract of cohabitation. Good-bye. The 25th year, Tubi 21. I swear by king Ptolemy and queen Cleopatra his sister and their ancestors that I will act accordingly.</ab>
